<p>I'm in.</p>
<p><strong>Credentials:</strong> Either 10 or 11 SCP articles depending on how you count them. 9 tales. 1 GOI file, 3 Nexuses, and a miscellaneous article. Have been on the site for over a year.</p>
<p><strong>Contest related stuff:</strong> I've got an idea for a MTF, and can give you more info in a PM if you would like. Currently thinking about the possibility of doing this with exploration, slice of life, and serpent's hand articles. I'm not sure if I want to captain or not, but I can either take up the mantle or give it to someone else depending on how all the needs work out. I'm still open to hearing other team's ideas or requests to join a team.</p>

